---
import { CheckSquare, Compass, HardDrives } from '@phosphor-icons/react';
import StackBuilderYaml from '../../../components/StackBuilder/StackBuilderYaml.astro';
import Tag from '../../../components/Tag.astro';
import AiSectionHeader from './AiSectionHeader.astro';
---

<section class="main">
  <section>
    <AiSectionHeader>
      <HardDrives />
      <h2>AI for DevOps <Tag primary>Coming soon</Tag></h2>
      <p>
        We have created a platform where spinning up a new service is as-easy-as adding a single line to a config file. This enables AI to
        truly modify infrastucture on the fly, leading to blazingly fast development.
      </p>
    </AiSectionHeader>
    <ol class="chat">
      <li>Could you create a new Node.js microservice for proxying image requests?</li>
      <li>Certainly! Adding a new Node.js component to <code>diploi.yaml</code>...</li>
    </ol>
    <!-- <section>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong><CheckSquare /> AI should be a choice without lock-in.</strong>
          Current services ofter lock you in to their own AI implementation, without the possibility to use custom tools.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong><CheckSquare /> AI should know DevOps</strong>
          We are making quick progress with AI that helps you code, but they ofter ignore the DevOps parts. We believe AI should also know how
          to setup your dev environment.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong><CheckSquare /> AI should be a tool</strong>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section> -->
  </section>
  <aside>
    <StackBuilderYaml />
  </aside>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../../../styles/mixins';

  .main {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--max-width-page-section);

    > section {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }

    section {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    ul {
      > li {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.25rem;

        > svg {
          color: var(--color-primary);
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .chat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;

    > li {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      color: var(--color-text-primary);

      code {
        padding: 3px 4px 0 4px;
        font-size: 18px;
        background-color: var(--color-border);
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    }

    > li:first-of-type {
      align-self: flex-end;
      background-color: var(--color-border);
      border-top-right-radius: 0px;
    }

    > li:last-of-type {
      border-top-left-radius: 0px;
    }
  }
</style>
